review_blob: Big dark chocolate on the nose, some coffee, orange. Pronounced coffer bitterness, chocolate orange, well balanced hope profile. A big fan of the black IPA style and this is a favourite
beer_name: Firestone Walker Wookey Jack Black Rye IPA

review_blob: Rich dark brown colour, small off white head. Rich, sweet, nutty aroma. Bittersweet hazelnut and praline taste. Sweet on the palate. Smooth nutty finish. A very quoffable brown beer.
